{"tid":1031791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秘魯豪華酒店遇襲 10槍手殺導遊挾持41港團友","createTime":"2019-02-22T01:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T02:17:07.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb807b2af6cc3ed035ef99905f19413155676f71","tid":1031791,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E8%B1%AA%E8%8F%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-10%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%BA%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A%E6%8C%BE%E6%8C%8141%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%98%E5%8F%8B-230358147.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%2598%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-10%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%258C%25BE%25E6%258C%258141%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%258F%258B-230358147.html&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=8e63775d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E8%B1%AA%E8%8F%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-10%E6%A7%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%BA%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A%E6%8C%BE%E6%8C%8141%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%98%E5%8F%8B-230358147.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F8IwJy4e9zqQMxCzsfhS1Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MzM4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/1b1349b37b3cca6477cbdce172de37c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF8IwJy4e9zqQMxCzsfhS1Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MzM4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F1b1349b37b3cca6477cbdce172de37c7&h=67a856fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n閉路電視畫面顯示，槍手闖入酒店範圍。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n更多<br />\n來自捷旅假期及尊賞假期兩個本港旅行團在秘魯遇劫，四十一名港人遭槍匪挾持，其中兩人失護照及手機。事發於當地時間本周二晚上，數名蒙面槍手闖入東部一間豪華酒店連開多槍，挾持酒店旅客，一名導遊中槍身亡，劫匪行兇後逃逸。香港旅遊業議會證實兩個旅行團受影響，目前全部人安全繼續行程，但其中捷旅假期有兩名團員遭槍匪搶走護照及手機。本港旅遊業界則認為事件屬單一事件，不會對南美團造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lF9g29zphLFOkklliFxJtw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NTUz/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/4a5da59e305e966ca76161031e0c7fbc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlF9g29zphLFOkklliFxJtw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NTUz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F4a5da59e305e966ca76161031e0c7fbc&h=d8464fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事件中遇害的秘魯導遊。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n更多<br />\n事發於秘魯東部馬德雷德迪奧斯大區（Madre de Dios）酒店Inkaterra Reserva Amazonica，與玻利維亞的邊境相距約廿公里，當地時間本周二晚上八時廿分，十名持槍歹徒闖入搶劫挾持酒店旅客，事件中一名秘魯籍導遊死亡，劫匪殺人及搶奪財物後逃逸。中國駐秘魯大使館昨證實，當時酒店內有兩個由香港出發、合共有四十一名遊客的旅行團，沒有任何中國人傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n香港旅遊業議會總幹事陳張樂怡證實，事發時兩個本港旅行團身處秘魯涉事酒店，分別是捷旅假期廿七天南美遊及尊賞假期卅四天南美遊，分別有廿一名及廿名港人團員及領隊。其中捷旅假期的旅行團有一名旅客被劫匪搶去護照，另一名旅客被搶去手機，被搶護照的旅客需留在秘魯補辦證件，其餘團員繼續行程，昨日已到玻利維亞，而尊賞假期旅行團亦繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n有團友遭搶劫的捷旅假期，其總經理周永強轉述事發經過時指，當地晚上時間十時許，旅行團在酒店內聽到槍聲，當地職員隨即要他們到廚房內躲避。領隊及團友也被持槍劫匪打劫，匪徒搶走兩名團友的護照、手機及袋後離去，當地警員在約一小時後到達。事發後有部分團友感到害怕，但會繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n10個槍匪41個人先搶到2部手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2b66d463478844a27fac38a6339873f4c22acd","tid":1031791,"uid":11706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔緊要！仲有心情繼續行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c94920ed9634f4aa807187219e9dacbade2dcfc","tid":1031791,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c2b66d463478844a27fac38a6339873f4c22acd","tid":1031791,"uid":11706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔緊要！仲有心情繼續行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"單一事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}